description:
EKHO IS EARTHS MIRROR WORLD. We find our cities and our countries, only different: electricity doesnt exist, dragons replace airliners, subway cars run on the backs of strange centipedes... But the most amazing are THE PRESHAUNS who, under an air of formal fluff, seem to hold the reins of the world. A student, Fourmille, and Yuri, in the neighbouring seat of a 747 bound for NEW YORK, find themselves propelled to EKHO and must learn to find their place in this new world. This becomes more complicated when Fourmille finds herself inhabited by the ghost of her dead aunt...
